9
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,900
Ja nikada nisam imao.

10
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,700
- Je li sve poneo?
- Naravno, i ne treba mu puno.

11
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:09,800
- Sta si mislio time, "i ne treba mu puno"?
- Pa, oni ce mu dati sve sto treba-

12
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,700
odecu, namirnice, i tako to.

13
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:14,200
Njemu treba ono sto sam mu ja dala.

14
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:17,500
Vreme je za autobus, momce.
Ne zelis da propustis taj voz.

15
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:28,000
- Cao, Mama.
- Srecno, Sine.

16
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:12,500
Podjimo.

17
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:19,200
Pomeri se, sine.
Povuci se. Povuci se.

18
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:22,400
- Iznesite! Iznesite!
- Naslonite na zid.

19
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,200
Ima nekoga gore.

20
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:23,100
- Idemo.
- Povucite ta creva! Nazad! Nazad!

21
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:26,600
U redu, cuvajte se!
Rusi se! Rusi se!

22
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:40,000
Zao mi je, momce. Upravo si ga propustio.

23
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:01,500
Idi i naspavaj se malo.
Ja cu zavrsiti ovde.

24
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:30,500
Okupili smo se ovde,
draga i voljena braco po Hristu...

25
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,800
da ovo dete bude ponovo rodjeno...

26
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:36,300
i primljeno u porodicu 
Hristove crkve...

27
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:40,000
zahvalimo svemogucem Bogu
za ove blagodeti...

28
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:44,000
i da, svi zajedno,
pomolimo se Bogu za njega...

29
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:47,700
da ovo dete do kraja svog zivota bude 
prosvetljno prema ovom novom pocetku.

30
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:10,300
Jesi li ti za kamp?
Hej, ti!

31
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:13,700
- Jesi li ti za kamp?
- Jesam.

32
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:17,100
Malo si zakasnio, sinko.
Ostali su stigli sinoc.

33
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:18,800
Znam.

34
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:21,000
Uhvatilo te bombardovanje, eh?

35
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:23,200
- Da.
- Oh, pa, nema veze, sinko.

36
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:27,600
Moraces da pesacis.
Nema puno milja.

37
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:30,500
Spusti kofer dole.

38
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:32,900
- Ime?
- Tomas Bedous.

39
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,700
Gospodine.

40
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,300
- Tomas Bedous, gospodine.
- Kasnis.

41
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,200
I... stoj!

42
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:54,100
I... stoj!

43
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,700
Ko si ti?

44
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:04,100
- Tomas Bedous, gospodine.
- Da li ti licim na oficira?

45
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:06,200
- Napred, mars!
- Ne, gospodine.

46
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:08,900
Ne zovi me "gospodine" onda.

47
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:11,600
Ko ti je dozvolio da upadnes ovde?

48
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,700
- Da sta?
- Da udjes ovde.

49
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:16,800
Da udjes u sobu.
Da otvoris vrata i da izvedes ulazak.

50
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:21,400
- Niko.
- Uradi to onda kako treba.

51
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:23,900
Izadji napolje, kucaj.

52
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:27,000
I kad ja kazem "da,"
udji i kazi, "Trazim dozvolu za ulaz."

53
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,900
Hajde.

54
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:38,200
Bedous.

55
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:40,900
Tvoj kofer... uzmi ga.

56
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:56,300
Da?

57
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:03,700
- Ko si ti?
- Bedous. Trazim dozvolu za ulaz.

58
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:06,600
Udji, Redove Bedous.

59
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:09,700
Mozes uzeti onaj.

60
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:20,700
Ostavi to.

61
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:24,200
Vec dovoljno kasnis.
Sledece po redu je sisanje.

62
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:27,400
Naci ces berbernicu
odmah pored kancelarije cete.

63
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:30,100
- Sledeci!
- Stani mirno. Stani mirno.

64
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,800
Stani mirno.. Sledeci.

65
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:35,300
Sledeci. Ime?

66
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:37,300
- Bedous, gospodine.
- Malo si mrsav, zar ne?

67
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,300
Da, gospodine.

68
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,300
- Imas li kasalj?
- Ne, gospodine.

69
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:45,000
- U redu. Obuci se tamo.
- Sledeci.

70
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,900
- Hocete li me ubosti time?
- Ruku, molim.

71
00:13:57,200 --> 00:14:00,100
Osecas li se bolje?

72
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:02,400
Ne volim igle.

73
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:05,900
Je li to sve?
Ja ne volim celu smrdljivu vojsku.

74
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:10,100
Svi regruti, poredjajte se pored vrata.
Postrojite se. Pokret!

75
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:13,300
Dobro!
Abrahams, Arlot, Bedous!

76
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:16,700
Malkolm, Partridz Silver, Jang.

77
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:19,200
Dobro. Da vas vidim.

78
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:36,700
Mozes li mi reci sta imas tu?

79
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:41,500
Jedan par gaca, P.T.
Jedan par gaca, kruzne.

80
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:44,200
Jedna balaklava.
Jedan par tregera. Jedan par cizama.

81
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:46,400
Veliki kaput, carape, prsluci, dokolenice.

82
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,800
Tvrda tkanina,
malo i veliko pakovanje.

83
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,900
Ratnicka odora, gas maska.

84
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:56,000
Porcija, cutura,
noz, viljuska i kasika.

85
00:14:57,400 --> 00:15:00,000
Nesto jos osim toga?

86
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:02,000
Mislim da ne.

87
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,100
Sta je to?

88
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,200
To je kanap za ciscenje puske.

89
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:10,300
Ucis.

90
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:14,400
U redu, svi vi!

91
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:17,900
Ima da odrzavate ovaj pod tako blistavim
da me zaslepi, i ima da pocnete upravo sad!

92
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,600
Hajde da odmah rascistimo dve stvari!

93
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:25,200
Prva stvar:
Komanda, "Voljno."

94
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:27,800
Necete se pokretati ni malo...

95
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:30,600
dok ne izgovorim tu komandu!

96
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:34,500
Necete se vrpoljiti,
okretati ili bilo sta drugo!

97
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,600
- Je li to jasno?
- Da, kaplare!

98
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:39,100
- Je li to jasno??
- Da, kaplare!

99
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:43,900
Ustaj! Umivanje! Brijanje! Oblaci se!

100
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
Ocistite ovu sobu u baraci,
i to hocu tako da sija!

101
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:48,300
- Jedan!
- Dva!
- Tri!

102
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,200
- Cetiri!
- Pet!
- Sest!

103
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:51,900
- Sedam!
- Osam!
- Devet!

104
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,500
- Deset!
- Jedanaest!
- Dvanaest!

105
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:57,700
Neparni brojevi, jedan korak napred!

106
00:15:57,800 --> 00:16:02,200
Parni brojevi, jedan korak nazad!

107
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,300
- Mars!
- Jedan, dva!

108
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:06,600
- Jang, koliko ceta ima u jednom bataljonu?
- Cetiri cete.

109
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:10,300
- Bedous, ime bataljonskog narednika.
- Bataljonski narednik Palmer.

110
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:13,900
- Tacno! Ima li pitanja?
- Bataljon je osnovan 1685.

111
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,000
- Da.
- Zbog cega?

112
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,800
Mislim, da li je bilo nekog posebnog razloga?

113
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:23,100
- Sta ti mislis?
- Ne znam.

114
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,600
Da zadivi Francuze!

115
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:29,500
U redu. Da pogledamo sta ste uradili 
do sada. Stanite pored svojih kreveta!

116
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:49,400
Dobro! Sada, pocecemo sve 
iz pocetka, hocemo li?

117
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:51,700
- Broji!
- Jedan, dva, tri! Jedan!

118
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:54,700
Ne mrdaj! Savrseno ne mrdaj!

119
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:57,800
Formiraj liniju po tri! Brzo.

120
00:16:57,900 --> 00:16:59,900
Mars! Centar. Pozadi.

121
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,300
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

122
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:04,600
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

123
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:06,900
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

124
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:09,100
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

125
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:12,200
Ispred. Pozadi. I popuni tu.

126
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,400
Dobro!

127
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:17,400
- Okret!
- Jedan, dva...

128
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,700
Sada se razmaknite! Hajde, brze!

129
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:23,400
U visini ruku, tvoje desno!
Pogled na desno!

130
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:25,800
Dizi ruku.

131
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:29,000
... napred!

132
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:39,800
- Bedous, zar ne?
- Da, gospodine.

133
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:42,300
Sta nisi dobro uradio, Bedous?

134
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:47,900
Izgleda da sam propustio da izbelim 
pojas ispod kopce, gospodine.

135
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:50,700
- Sredi to sledeci put.
- Da, gospodine.

136
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:53,900
Na desno! Brzo marsiranje!

137
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:57,300
Leva, desna! Leva, desna! Sad!

138
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:59,300
Odred!

139
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,500
- Stoj!
- Leva, jedan, dva!

140
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:05,800
Sta to, dodjavola, radis, Bedous?
Pomeri se jako nazad!

141
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:11,200
Uvrci! Uvrci!

142
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:13,100
Pocepaj ga!

143
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:23,300
Hajde! Hajde! Drzite ruke gore!

144
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:26,200
- Jebem mu, prodji izmedju--
- Vhoa!

145
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:29,900
Ne gledaj dole. Ne gledaj dole!
Prokleta budalo!

146
00:18:30,100 --> 00:18:34,000
Hajde! Hajde!
Plasite se da ne pokvasite noge?

147
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:39,400
Pazite da vam te puske ostanu suve!

148
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:42,300
Penji se uz te proklete merdevine!

149
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:49,400
Hajde! Sta mislis da je ovo, izlet?

150
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:53,900
Hajde!
Ustaj, ti blesavi stvore!

151
00:18:57,700 --> 00:19:00,800
Hajde! Jos niste zavrsili!

152
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,100
Jebem ti. Moram da zapalim.

153
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:22,000
Oni su ispred.

154
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:25,100
Pa, ti produzi.
Ja cu da zastanem da zapalim.

155
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:48,300
- Mrzim ovaj rat.
- Preboleces.

156
00:19:51,300 --> 00:19:54,800
Ne, nije to u pitanju.
Moja devojka.

157
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:58,600
Verili smo se, znas, i onda...

158
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:03,500
i kada su me mobilisali,
pa...

159
00:20:03,600 --> 00:20:05,600
njen stari mi nije
dozvolio da je ozenim.

160
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:09,000
Nek ide bestraga.

161
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:12,500
Rekao je da treba da 
sacekamo dok ne dobijemo rat.

162
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:14,500
Kopile.

163
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:20,100
Dozvolio bi da mu Svabe tucaju zenu
cim bi mu pokucali na vrata.

164
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,000
Zeleo sam da letim.

165
00:20:35,900 --> 00:20:37,800
Nisam prosao lekarski.

166
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:41,300
Nisam znao za to.

167
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:48,000
- Ko tebe ceka kod kuce, Tomi?
- Koga ja imam?

168
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:52,600
Pa, tu su mama i tata, predpostavljam.

169
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:54,800
I Tina.

170
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:58,000
Dobro za tebe, druze.

171
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:00,000
Pusti me da pogadjam.

172
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:03,500
Ona ima smedju kosu, braon oci...

173
00:21:03,700 --> 00:21:06,500
belu kozu, lepe sise, tacno?

174
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:10,000
Tina je koker spanijel.

175
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:15,600
- Ona je divan pas.
- Kucka?

176
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:18,200
Da. Kucka.

177
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:30,900
Sta ces raditi kada se sve ovo zavrsi?

178
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:35,300
Oh, ne znam.

179
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:39,000
Ja imam planove.

180
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:42,000
Garaza, druze.

181
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:45,600
Kupicu garazu negde ovde u blizini
u bacicu se na posao secenja metala.

182
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:48,400
- Sta kazes na to da se udruzis sa mnom, Tom?
- Hej. Trebalo bi da krenemo.

183
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:58,100
Izlazis sutra sa mnom i sa momcima?

184
00:21:58,200 --> 00:22:01,100
Proslavljamo... kraj obuke.

185
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:04,800
Pab je pun poslepodne,
uvece je prava ludnica.

186
00:22:04,900 --> 00:22:06,900
Dobro. Dobro. vazi.

187
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:10,600
O cemu je film?

188
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:14,100
Zaboravi slike, druze.
U pitanju je zena.

189
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:18,600
Sesces pored dobrog komada u poslednjim redovima,
i otici cete pre nego sto se i pojavi naslov filma.

190
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:22,700
Oh, za Bozje zdravlje.

191
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:26,900
- Imaju bar 10 minuta prednosti.
- Mislis?

192
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:29,200
Nema prokletog provoda za nas veceras.

193
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:34,400
- Idem dole.
- Sta, dole nizbrdo?

194
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:36,200
Da.

195
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:39,200
Hej! Nemoj to da radis.
Ubices se.

196
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:11,900
- Da li ga je pregledao vojni lekar.?
- Vojni lekar je rekao da nema potrebe za lecenjem, gospodine.

197
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:13,800
Zatvorenik i pratnja...

198
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:17,100
i... okret!

199
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:22,100
Zatvorenik i pratnja, brzi mars!

200
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:24,800
Leva, desna! Leva, desna!

201
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:26,900
Zatvorenik i pratnja, stoj!

202
00:24:42,300 --> 00:24:44,500
Redove Bedous, ulazi!

203
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:53,000
U 0900 casova, vi cete paradno
proci kroz glavnu kapiju...

204
00:24:53,100 --> 00:24:56,100
gde cete sacekati transport
koji ce vas odvesti u vase jedinice.

205
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:58,400
Vraticete se ovde do 2100 sati...

206
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:01,800
ili vas rodjena majka nece prepoznati
kad ja budem zavrsio sa vama.

207
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:04,300
Zaboravite sve sto sam vam rekao
i nece vas biti u blizini...

208
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:07,200
- Utesno, zar ne?
- ...da mi napisete pismo zahvalnosti
kada se rat bude zavrsio.

209
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:10,100
Saljes signale, Bedous?

210
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,400
Samo za "pobedu," kaplare.

211
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:18,100
Ovo je Muviton.

212
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,100
Lezi dole tamo! Lezi dole!

213
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,700
- Zdravo, Dzek.
- Sve moramo sami, zar ne?

214
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:27,100
Ti si usamljenicka vrsta
cudaka, zar ne?

215
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:30,600
